    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "The life of Jesus, now too, becomes clearer when these things are re-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "membered. His powers of levitation, His ability to pass through doors,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "walk on water, and heal the sick are the essential attributes of men",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "from outer space. They will also be ours someday when we will be \"free",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "like birds\" (Ezk. 13:20). At Jesus' birth the celestial army came quite",
