      "text": "of the Lord, with the usual signs of His presence, shone around them.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "There was a multitude of the heavenly army with this space-man. And",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
