      "text": "men live, and we too will someday live.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "This clear understanding of things as they are and as they will be, is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
